## Errors & Mistakes
The previous amended commit was technically more robust against future Torch base images that already include 10.3 or 10.3a, but it made the sed much harder to read. The user preferred the simpler expression. That means this version is intentionally not idempotent for a hypothetical future base list that already includes 10.3 or 10.3a; a future maintainer should revisit the expression if the base image's TORCH_CUDA_ARCH_LIST changes.

